    "attributes": {
        "action": "Review sentences and punishments for sexual assault and rape cases",
        "additional_details": "Sex offences should receive longer sentences similar to manslaughter and murder due to the severe, lasting harm they cause, often resulting in lifelong trauma. Stronger penalties could reflect the seriousness of the crime, deter offenders, protect the public, and maintain trust in the justice system while still allowing for proportionate sentencing and rehabilitation.",
        "background": "Introduce stronger sentences for sexual assault and rape on par with manslaughter and murder. Review training for investigators to ensure better survivor support and a justice system that ensures accountability, deterrence, and long-term public protection.",
